Index >  PDFProducer

PDFProducer

Description

Returns or sets the name of the application that generated the PDF document.

Data type

<string>

Syntax

.PDFProducer = 'Dynamic Web TWAIN';

Remarks

When an error occurs, check ErrorCode or ErrorString for error information.
